title: Yamaha Expands Offerings for Vinyl Lovers in the Smart Home: Introducing the MusicCast VINYL 500 Wi-Fi Turntable in White
title_detail_value: Yamaha Expands Offerings for Vinyl Lovers in the Smart Home: Introducing the MusicCast VINYL 500 Wi-Fi Turntable in White
published_parsed: time.struct_time(tm_year=2019, tm_mon=11, tm_mday=5, tm_hour=11, tm_min=0, tm_sec=0, tm_wday=1, tm_yday=309, tm_isdst=0)
summary:
The Yamaha MusicCast VINYL 500 turntable combines classic Hi-Fi playback with Wi-Fi streaming to satisfy the resurgent interest in vinyl and bring the turntable into the modern era. Now with a white version, it’s never been easier for enthusiasts to integrate their love of vinyl with their home decor and entertainment setup. The MusicCast VINYL 500 supports wireless playback to other rooms with MusicCast-enabled speakers, offers built-in streaming services and works with the most popular voice control assistants.

(PRWeb November 05, 2019)

Read the full story at https://www.prweb.com/releases/yamaha_expands_offerings_for_vinyl_lovers_in_the_smart_home_introducing_the_musiccast_vinyl_500_wi_fi_turntable_in_white/prweb16698464.htm

title: Emerald Professional Protection Products Reports - China Tariffs Start to Bite Infection Control Industry
title_detail_value: Emerald Professional Protection Products Reports - China Tariffs Start to Bite Infection Control Industry
published_parsed: time.struct_time(tm_year=2019, tm_mon=11, tm_mday=5, tm_hour=8, tm_min=0, tm_sec=0, tm_wday=1, tm_yday=309, tm_isdst=0)
summary:
As everyone is no doubt aware by now, the US trade administration has imposed additional tariffs on a wide range of disposable products from China. As older inventories carried by importers begin to run out, users of infection control and hygiene products are getting serious sticker shock. Most costs have gone up by 15-25%. These single-use essentials are not easily manufactured elsewhere outside of China as they are labor intensive and low margin items.

(PRWeb November 05, 2019)

Read the full story at https://www.prweb.com/releases/emerald_professional_protection_products_reports_china_tariffs_start_to_bite_infection_control_industry/prweb16683057.htm
